arks I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 344, \"to\": 607, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 355, \"end\": 361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicola_Roberts\", \"score\": 0.9999999971105353, \"rank\": 2.8893572979165736e-09, \"text\": \"Nicola\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicola_Roberts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicola_Roberts\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first female Olympic boxing gold medallist\", \"from\": 375, \"to\": 421}, {\"ngram\": \"London\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 431}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 447, \"to\": 454}, {\"ngram\": \"the next generation\", \"from\": 459, \"to\": 478}, {\"ngram\": \"new goals\", \"from\": 491, \"to\": 500}, {\"ngram\": \"bookmarks\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 523}, {\"ngram\": \"offers\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 563}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 571}, {\"ngram\": \"updates\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 583}, {\"ngram\": \"The Independent\", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 604}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice Nicola Adamssays it is a \\\"dream come true\\\" to have inspired thenext generation of female boxersas they prepare to showcase their talent at the ParisOlympics.\", \"from\": 608, \"to\": 789, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy notice\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 630}, {\"ngram\": \"Nicola\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 637}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"dream\", \"from\": 654, \"to\": 662}, {\"ngram\": \"thenext generation\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 709}, {\"ngram\": \"female boxersas\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 728}, {\"ngram\": \"their talent\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 766}, {\"ngram\": \"the ParisOlympics\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 787}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Adams has always been a trendsetter.\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 827, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Adams\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 796}, {\"ngram\": \"a trendsetter\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 826}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From being the only girl in her boxing gym when she first put on the gloves, to becoming the first female boxer to represent England, and thencapitalising when boxing first became an Olympic sport.\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 1025, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 953, \"end\": 960, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.994726824851636, \"rank\": 0.0052978967531575, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the only girl\", \"from\": 839, \"to\": 852}, {\"ngram\": \"her boxing gym\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 870}, {\"ngram\": \"the gloves\", \"from\": 893, \"to\": 903}, {\"ngram\": \"the first female boxer\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 939}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic sport\", \"from\": 1008, \"to\": 1024}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Women's boxing made its debut at London 2012 and she sealed her place in history by becoming the first woman to win an Olympic boxing gold medal, changing not only her life but the entire profile of the sport in the United Kingdom.\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1060, \"end\": 1071, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999719747332118, \"rank\": 2.8026050303163066e-05, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1243, \"end\": 1257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999361198226, \"rank\": 5.908870434270819e-08, \"text\": \"United Kingdom\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Women's boxing\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1041}, {\"ngram\": \"its debut\", \"from\": 1047, \"to\": 1056}, {\"ngram\": \"her place\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1096}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1107}, {\"ngram\": \"the first woman\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1135}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic boxing gold medal\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1171}, {\"ngram\": \"not only her life\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1199}, {\"ngram\": \"the entire profile\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1222}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1235}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Boxing has been and still is everything to me.\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1307, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Boxing\", \"from\": 1261, \"to\": 1267}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1300}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's shaped who I am and it gave me a platform to break barriers for women's sport,\\\" Adams tellsThe Independent.\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1420, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a platform\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1354}, {\"ngram\": \"barriers\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1372}, {\"ngram\": \"women's sport\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1390}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not just a sport, it's a way of life that taught me discipline and resilience and the importance of fighting for what you believe in.\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1561, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just a sport\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1444}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1456}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1464}, {\"ngram\": \"discipline\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1490}, {\"ngram\": \"resilience\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1505}, {\"ngram\": \"the importance\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1524}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's just been incredibly gratifying and humbling to know that I have inspired the next generation of female boxers and seeing young girls lace up and put thei