l\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2200}, {\"ngram\": \"my boxing club\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2218}, {\"ngram\": \"at least a good 10 years\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2247}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's changed so much now and it's so good to see because I feel like when the Olympics is on, it's the only time that you see lots of different sports that have women involved besides the more common ones like football and boxing.\\\"\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2492, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2347}, {\"ngram\": \"the only time\", \"from\": 2360, \"to\": 2373}, {\"ngram\": \"lots\", \"from\": 2387, \"to\": 2391}, {\"ngram\": \"different sports\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2411}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 2422, \"to\": 2427}, {\"ngram\": \"the more common ones\", \"from\": 2445, \"to\": 2465}, {\"ngram\": \"football\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2479}, {\"ngram\": \"boxing\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2490}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Adams defended her Olympic gold at the 2016 Games in Rio, becoming the first British boxer to retain an Olympic title since Harry Mallin in 1924.\", \"from\": 2494, \"to\": 2639, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2547, \"end\": 2550, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9983617683225978, \"rank\": 0.0016409198794883155, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2571, \"end\": 2578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.7202033841611306, \"rank\": 0.387210269681826, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}, {\"begin\": 2618, \"end\": 2630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Mallin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"